  <h1>Appendix G&nbsp; &mdash; AI Assistance Disclaimer</h1>
  <table class=callout><tr><td class=c-info>
    AITAS uses artificial intelligence to <b>draft</b> test cases, scripts, and healing
    suggestions. All AI-generated content is clearly identified and must be
    <b>reviewed and approved by a qualified person</b> before it is relied upon. AI
    output may contain errors and does not constitute validation. The deploying
    organization retains full responsibility for verification, validation, and regulatory
    compliance.
  </td></tr></table>

